{"word":"παιδίον","slug":"παιδίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παιδίον</b></el> <el>(παιδίον, ου, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <a href='S:παῖς'><el>παῖς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a little</i> or <i>young child</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a slave-lad</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}